## Career Affinity (RIASEC) Codes

Affinity results use Holland Code letters: **R**ealistic, **I**nvestigative, **A**rtistic, **S**ocial, **E**nterpreneurial, **C**onventional. Only 13.2% of sessions (2,015) produce an affinity result. Top codes among completers:

`ISC` (71), `ICR` (55), `ICA` (49), `IRC` (46), `ICS` (45), `EIS` (42), `IRS` (39)

Investigative (I) leads most combinations, suggesting the user base skews toward analytical/academic orientations.

